          "en": "giving away … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:3.26",
          "pli": "paṭinissaggāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. ",
          "en": "For the letting go of negligence, these three things should be developed.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:4.1",
          "pli": "Idamavoca bhagavā. ",
          "en": "That is what the Buddha said. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:4.2",
          "pli": "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. ",
          "en": "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:4.3",
          "pli": "Rāgapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:5.1",
          "pli": "Rāgaṃ dosañca mohañca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:5.2",
          "pli": "kodhūpanāhapañcamaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:5.3",
          "pli": "Makkhapaḷāsaissā ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:5.4",
          "pli": "maccharimāyāsāṭheyyā. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:6.1",
          "pli": "Thambhasārambhamānañca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:6.2",
          "pli": "atimānamadassa ca; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:6.3",
          "pli": "Pamādā sattarasa vuttā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:6.4",
          "pli": "rāgapeyyālanissitā. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:7.1",
          "pli": "Ete opammayuttena, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:7.2",
          "pli": "āpādena abhiññāya; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:7.3",
          "pli": "Pariññāya parikkhayā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:7.4",
          "pli": "pahānakkhayabbayena; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:7.5",
          "pli": "Virāganirodhacāgaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:7.6",
          "pli": "paṭinissagge ime dasa. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:8.1",
          "pli": "Suññato animitto ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:8.2",
          "pli": "appaṇihito ca tayo; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:8.3",
          "pli": "Samādhimūlakā peyyā—",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:8.4",
          "pli": "lesupi vavatthitā cāti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:8.5",
          "pli": "Tatiyo paṇṇāsako niṭṭhito. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an3.183-352:8.6",
          "pli": "Tikanipātapāḷi niṭṭhitā. ",
          "en": "The Book of the Threes is finished."
        }
